data.description: Embrace contemporary comfort in this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, featuring a versatile bonus room. Enjoy upgrades including kitchen, bathrooms, floors, windows, doors, and more! The bonus room, now a cozy man cave, can easily adapt to your needs with direct access to the driveway! Outside, take advantage of the screened lanai and shady back yard. With key items like AC, water heater, and drain field being newer, this home is ready for your personal touches.
